0x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于希望恢复<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-global-offensive"><em>《反恐精英：全球攻势》</em></a>的粉丝的大量负面评论<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-2"><em>，《反恐精英 2》</em></a>目前是<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/brands">Steam</a>上评价最低的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/valve">Valve</a>游戏。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/persona-3-reload-preview-hands-on-gameplay-3490210">《女神异闻录 3：重装上阵》预览：黑暗时刻看起来比以往任何时候都更好</a></strong></li></ul><p>需要澄清的是，在撰写本文时（10 月 10 日），该游戏的评论“褒贬不一”，虽然这不是明确的负面结果，但它低于<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dota-2">Dota 2</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/half-life">Half-Life</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/half-life-2">Half-Life 2</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/portal">Portal</a> 、 Portal 2</em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/left-4-dead"><em>留下 4 人死亡</em></a>。</p><p>将最近所有这些评论联系在一起的一个问题是， <em>《反恐精英：全球攻势》</em>随着<em>《反恐精英 2》的推出而被推翻。</em> </p><figure id="attachment_3512486" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3512486" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3512486" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3512486" class="wp-caption-text"> 《反恐精英 2》来源：Valve</figcaption></figure><p>由于<em>《反恐精英 2》</em>并不是官方续作，而是被描述为游戏对 Valve Source 2 引擎的免费升级， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-players-criticise-missing-csgo-game-modes-3507697">因此<em>《全球攻势》</em>中的几乎所有内容都可以在新版本中使用</a>。</p><p>然而，军备竞赛、飞行侦察兵和危险地带等模式以及竞技地图和僚机地图、车间地图以及 Mac 和 Linux 支持都未能在升级中幸存。</p><p>这些遗漏加上<em>《反恐精英：全球攻势》</em>现在可以作为离线“演示”来玩的事实，证明了许多不满的粉丝。</p><p> “我10年前就买了<em>CS:GO</em> ，为什么现在被<em>CS2</em>取代了？！”<a href="https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561197990803338/recommended/730/">在他们的负面评论中问道</a>。 “当我不在的时候，宜家从来没有进过我家，用他们认为更好的黄色扶手椅替换我的黑色椅子！” </p><figure id="attachment_3512488" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3512488" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3512488" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-worst-rated-valve-game-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w"